<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Categories - RishiVerse</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: rgb(255 241 196);
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/layout') %> <!-- Include Navbar -->

    <main class="flex-1 ml-20 p-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Explore Indian Cultural Genres</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-center text-gray-600 mb-8">Discover books from ancient scriptures, mythology, and historical texts.</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <!-- Category Links -->
            <a href="/books/ancient-scriptures" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">📜 Ancient Scriptures</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Vedas, Upanishads, and Puranas.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/mythology" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">🕉️ Mythology</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Stories from Ramayana & Mahabharata.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/history" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">🏰 Indian History</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Ancient and medieval historical texts.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/literature" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">📖 Literature</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Classic works of Kalidasa, Tulsidas, and more.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/spirituality-yoga" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">🧘 Spirituality & Yoga</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Bhagavad Gita, Yoga Sutras, and meditation.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/ayurveda" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">🌿 Ayurveda</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Charaka Samhita & Sushruta Samhita.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/vedic-science" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">🔭 Vedic Science</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Astronomy, mathematics, and ancient knowledge.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/art-music" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">🎭 Art & Music</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Natya Shastra, classical dance, and music.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/books/philosophy" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer block">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">📚 Philosophy</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Advaita Vedanta, Jainism, and Buddhism.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
